name: Prototype - Photographer in a forest
description:
School project - Alt-Tab to close the game after you're done there isn't a quit game feature yet! WASD movement. When you've taken pictures in the game they'll end up in a folder called "Screenshots" in your C: Drive

Feedback -  https://forms.gle/sgFsqBc6VgawPKdM7

Here is a google form, we would really appreciate it if you took the time and did it. We need the feedback for our school project. They're in Swedish so if you don't know Swedish use google translate!
